Text:
Amazing torrent! Thanks so much for this. I've already uploaded it a full time, and I'm still seeding it for a while! 

If you're interested in hearing something really interesting related to the Beatles, check out my torrent called "Cracked Pepper". It's a really well-done Sgt. Pepper mashup album. Not that garbage mashup with Pet Sounds, this one is actually really amazing for the most part. Take care!
